# ============================================================
#  MAIZE LEAF DISEASE DETECTION PROTOTYPE
#  ConvNeXtTiny Training Script — Kaggle Notebook Version
#
#  Dataset  : Consolidated Corn Dataset (yasirahmad0810)
#  Classes  : Blight | Common_Rust | Grey_Leaf_Spot | Healthy
#  Platform : Kaggle (T4 GPU x2)
#  Split    : 70% Train / 15% Validation / 15% Test
#
#  HOW TO USE:
#  1. Add these datasets to your Kaggle notebook:
#     - yasirahmad0810/consolidated-corn-dataset
#     - your convnext-weights dataset (convnext_tiny_notop.h5)
